= SDL_EnableScreenSaver =

Allow the screen to be blanked by a screen saver.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void SDL_EnableScreenSaver(void);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 2.0.0.

